OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Falthough some misty low cloud possible
OL,9,Fin the east. Cold with perhaps a touch
OL,10,Fof frost possible in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FDry and mostly sunny
OL,13,Falthough some patchy low cloud may
OL,14,Flinger along the coast. Warm across
OL,15,Fthe west but cooler in the east with
OL,16,Fan onshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
